gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e393f15c38ed8cb0e911a4d71db9481dfd35fc38","tid":2006514,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9e5da3385f6b1cccad2db5bdb5dffe752cce2c","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"佢帶我去到一間好大好靚的房間。<br />\n<br />\n「你間屋得一間房？」我好奇咁問。<br />\n<br />\n佢笑左笑，講：「呢度係酒店式住宅黎。」<br />\n<br />\n因為得一張凳，唔夠兩個人坐，所以我地都坐左喺床沿。<br />\n<br />\n佢拉開窗簾，一覽無遺嘅夜景盡收眼底，只見遠處點點的燈光，映照在水面上，波光粼粼，有種浪漫嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n佢拎左枝紅酒，斟左杯比我。<br />\n<br />\n「飲杯酒先啦。」佢好輕柔咁比左杯酒我。<br />\n<br />\n妖精有兩種模式，一種係妖精模式，一種係人類模式。妖精不受外界任何物質影響，但係一旦開啟人類模式，所感所想，同人類係一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n而且可以設定做不同的人類身份。為左可以更投入「考驗」，我選擇左開啟人類模式，而身份則設定係20歲未拍過拖的少女。模式最勁嘅地方係，可以根據返所設定嘅角色嘅心智同埋背景去思考。<br />\n<br />\n即係話，只要開啟人類模式，我就會心智同一個20歲未拍過拖嘅少女無異，同時喺期間，用唔到什何妖力。<br />\n<br />\n不過，為左避免有咩意外發生，我只係開啟左個模式20分鐘。模式有計時功能，一到20分鐘，就自動變返預設的妖精模式。"},{"pid":"d6cd2a59a5999050709aeb5972a980465d51f13e","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b90b556d94a0ea6cef5a044dd743776266b312bb","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4003f0314e7446c3aea83d57aef3edbc26ab2654","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f447c055a66d6c95689048e413f69894412fa419","tid":2006514,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"都留咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"笑，係我錯<br />\n<br />\n你想臭桃點謝罪？<br />\n<br />\n1. 更文   2. 切桃謝罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f427a43735df0a4b42b01d3ab98404f0b21de7bd","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6cd2a59a5999050709aeb5972a980465d51f13e","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b90b556d94a0ea6cef5a044dd743776266b312bb","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4003f0314e7446c3aea83d57aef3edbc26ab2654","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"都留咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"笑，係我錯<br />\n<br />\n你想臭桃點謝罪？<br />\n<br />\n1. 更文   2. 切桃謝罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁以後會變左臭<br />\n<br />\n無左桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab4acdc62297162854ee3e21d59c5396f799b9f","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f427a43735df0a4b42b01d3ab98404f0b21de7bd","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6cd2a59a5999050709aeb5972a980465d51f13e","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b90b556d94a0ea6cef5a044dd743776266b312bb","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"笑，係我錯<br />\n<br />\n你想臭桃點謝罪？<br />\n<br />\n1. 更文   2. 切桃謝罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁以後會變左臭<br />\n<br />\n無左桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"將個桃斬開一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變臭木兆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb27f30ef770037b089a9b342be5f170a117fb2","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"開啟左人類模式後的我，接過酒杯，飲左啖酒。<br />\n<br />\n「隻酒......點解好似......？」點解飲左一啖，就已經開始有醉意？<br />\n<br />\n眼前點點燈光愈黎愈朦朧，我覺得有少少暈。<br />\n<br />\n佢見我暈暈地，就扶一扶我，然後望住我，想kiss我。<br />\n<br />\n「等陣，會唔會太快？」我哋好似識左一日都未夠。<br />\n<br />\n佢望住我對眼，深情咁講：「因為你太吸引啦，我驚我會錯過你。」<br />\n<br />\n我心如鹿撞，依種就係戀愛？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪任務完成啦？<br />\n<br />\n我緊緊捉住佢隻手，問：「你鍾唔鍾意我？」<br />\n<br />\n佢情深咁答：「鍾意。我未試過咁鍾意一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然一切黎得太快，不過我感覺到佢眼神的真誠。<br />\n<br />\n佢輕吻我，然後慢慢將我壓落床。<br />\n<br />\n雙手開始喺我背部游離。<br />\n<br />\n「你真係鍾意我，先好掂我。」我喺佢耳邊講。<br />\n<br />\n「鍾意。我好鍾意你。」佢眼神充滿住貪婪，似乎好想得到我。<br />\n<br />\n依種感覺就係鍾意？我好疑惑。<br />\n<br />\n喺依個時候，20分鐘過去，我噠噠手指，用幻術滿足左佢的要求。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪？點解考官未出黎宣布我通過考驗？<br />\n<br />\n我好疑惑咁望住一面滿足、精疲力竭、訓喺床上嘅佢......"},{"pid":"0b256def739074e29eddbcd9d2a7c06e3786f270","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"無人...嗚嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd93755aaa0b6321dabae2df14ed0c5f4b8286fe","tid":2006514,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"幫你推!"},{"pid":"8715b9746c1ad62c0122d4634dac9db7e30b9c22","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd93755aaa0b6321dabae2df14ed0c5f4b8286fe","tid":2006514,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"幫你推!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"謝謝你，好難得先可以唔係負數"},{"pid":"b51ed314259cbef33d9f2827365e2c4dc15b156c","tid":2006514,"uid":253135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008d38410fe593cf1597259e91b64157cbd084a7","tid":2006514,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:31:32.000Z","msg":"睇緊架，正評左"},{"pid":"0fbc9c94699440a13931dd7a19d67b6328fcd43a","tid":2006514,"uid":71807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T20:56:19.000Z","msg":"推 唔出就綁住你放置play"},{"pid":"18b75bb45301b553f5980ff47e0ffde0bc986123","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb139b2515f1c4d767a8f9699b348b25720930f8","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"人地話，男人喺歡愉過後，就會筋疲力盡，抱頭大睡。<br />\n<br />\n我望住一臉滿足嘅佢，有少少疑惑：喱d......就係鍾意？<br />\n<br />\n點解考官未到嘅？未宣布我已經完成測試嘅？<br />\n<br />\n唔通因爲佢未承認佢鐘意我？定係因為我地未一齊？<br />\n<br />\n過左陣，佢醒左。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋......係咩關係？」我忍唔住問。<br />\n<br />\n「你想喺咩咪咩囉！靚女。」佢笑左笑。<br />\n<br />\n然後，寫左佢電話喺張紙上面比我。<br />\n<br />\n「我送你落去呀！」佢講。<br />\n<br />\n我突然發現，原來人類嘅愛情觀好扭曲，我同佢發生左關係（雖然只係幻術），但係我地連對方咩名都未知。<br />\n<br />\n「家姐。我想問點解考官未出現嘅？我同個個人.....已經做左咩啦喎。」我問。<br />\n<br />\n「男人同你做，唔代表鍾意你。事實上，只要有機會做，佢地都會做，唔理對你有無feel。而且，愈易得到，就愈唔會珍惜。」<br />\n<br />\n我好疑惑咁望住家姐。<br />\n<br />\n真咩？"},{"pid":"62e2adb5927982b818e7fa06daf83d0dee73f79a","tid":2006514,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666f390e809d89dee3c6a47dc1f0c66fe454497f","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T00:00:40.000Z","msg":"未見過志豪咁樣：交代頭條新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"285fa63f1829a13bca61977c6212072af64291bf","tid":2006514,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e1c6b8600404b0fcc930105a897900b0f1f58c5","tid":2006514,"uid":178900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9519d3c47b6103034f2def722ed3776812e6c1","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:27:31.000Z","msg":"家姐笑笑口，然後比我睇個男人做緊咩。<br />\n<br />\n個個男人喺酒吧度，同朋友傾計：「琴晚我屌左條女，個樣幾純品，對腳同波都好正。下次肚餓再搵佢。」<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅兄弟笑住話：「咁正？有無閃卡先？」<br />\n<br />\n「當然有啦！」但係個個男仔點搵，手機都唔見佢口入面的閃卡。<br />\n<br />\n家姐問：「你知道我無呃你啦？男人，你愈難得到，佢就愈珍惜。」<br />\n<br />\n我想開口反駁家姐。<br />\n<br />\n家姐就搶先講：「唔信？我示範下點令一個男人對你死心塌地。」<br />\n<br />\n講完，家姐就帶我去左一間婚紗舖。<br />\n<br />\n家姐話：「你眼前的情侶，由中學已經一齊，經歷過高考、搵工，同埋男方家人離開等等嘅事，拍左十幾年拖，而加終於訂婚。」<br />\n<br />\n我望住眼前的情侶，衷心祝福佢地，然後又疑惑問家姐：「咁佢地關我咩事？」<br />\n<br />\n「你信唔信，我可以令個男人死心塌地愛上我？」家姐問。<br />\n<br />\n「唔信。佢地經歷咁多，又咁多年感情，打風都打唔甩啦！」<br />\n<br />\n家姐無講野，憑空消失。"},{"pid":"f3d324f2354e94eecbe08f0c2d66bcab12981b88","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e1c6b8600404b0fcc930105a897900b0f1f58c5","tid":2006514,"uid":178900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"新讀者？"},{"pid":"572daa339a383a41a407a60d0a76b65ca83ad9b6","tid":2006514,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cfa219ec9299f94d819be1606c4f5366789870","tid":2006514,"uid":178900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3d324f2354e94eecbe08f0c2d66bcab12981b88","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e1c6b8600404b0fcc930105a897900b0f1f58c5","tid":2006514,"uid":178900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"新讀者？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7a9fe2914f3d1f7b9bbc32dc69193447bd905c","tid":2006514,"uid":142750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc038ec6714c0d1722f7bfeba4f47a59785de68f","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"家姐講：每個人都有一個心魔，令佢地永遠都得唔到真正口既幸福。而成功口既妖精，就係識用人口既心魔迷惑人。<br />\n<br />\n眼前的情侶經過起起落落，似乎打風都打唔甩，只係，無論幾堅固口既關係，都會有一個缺口。<br />\n<br />\n男口既叫Tim，女口既叫Amy。<br />\n<br />\nTim喺一間甲級商廈返工，平時生活規律，準時放工，又唔多出街，而且唔飲酒、唔食煙，喺一個好男人。<br />\n<br />\n家姐化身左做一個望落楚楚可憐，但係有一絲倔強口既女仔。佢話女仔唔駛靚，太靚，反而唔夠girlfriend able ，反而望落有幾分姿色，平易近人更加有market 。<br />\n<br />\n而勾引Tim，首先要知道佢的魔係咩。"},{"pid":"4772941961a68c65f42373cfebd35eae913c2738","tid":2006514,"uid":178900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"666f390e809d89dee3c6a47dc1f0c66fe454497f","tid":2006514,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T00:00:40.000Z","msg":"未見過志豪咁樣：交代頭條新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}